UID:A2ItQ1c8zLjtMaDoSOCyZ
SUMMARY:Free Introductory Improv Class ISSAQUAH
DTSTAMP:20260214T003617Z
DTSTART:20260215T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Have you always wanted to take an improv class\, but weren’t su
	re if you want to commit to a quarter-long term? We have the solution. Joi
	n us in Seattle on 2/20 at 7:00pm\n\n✨ Ever Thought About Trying Improv… B
	ut Weren’t Sure Where to Start? ✨ \n\nTotally get it—jumping into somethin
	g new can feel a lot. That’s why we’re hooking you up with a FREE Intro to
	 Improv Class made just for folks who are curious\, kinda nervous\, or jus
	t wanna try something different. 👀 \n\nHave you always wanted to take an i
	mprov class\, but weren’t sure if you wanted to commit to a quarter-long t
	erm? We have the solution. Join us in ISSAQUAH at our new eastside improv 
	school \n\n✨ Ever Thought About Trying Improv… But Weren’t Sure Where to S
	tart? ✨ \n\nTotally get it—jumping into something new can feel a lot. That
	’s why we’re hooking you up with a FREE Intro to Improv Class made just fo
	r folks who are curious\, kinda nervous\, or just wanna try something diff
	erent. 👀 \n\nNo experience? No stress. This class is 100% beginner-friendl
	y. Like\, truly. We’re talking zero pressure\, major good vibes. \n\nAt Un
	expected Productions—Seattle’s biggest & boldest improv school—we believe 
	everyone has a creative spark. Whether you wanna level up your communicati
	on game\, shake up your routine\, or just laugh for two hours straight wit
	h cool strangers\, we got you. 💥 \n\n🧠 You’ll learn how to stay in the mom
	ent\, trust your instincts\, and say “yes\, and…” to life\n\n🎭 You’ll be g
	uided by pros who make it all feel easy\, welcoming\, and seriously fun\n\
	n👯‍♀️ You’ll meet awesome people and maybe even surprise yourself \n\nBut hea
	ds up: we’re only offering 50 spots—and these go fast. So if your gut’s li
	ke “do ittt\,” listen to it. 😉 \n\n📅 Date: Sunday\, Feb. 15\, 2026\n\n🕒 Ti
	me: 11:00am – 1:00pm\n\n📍 Location: Improv School Eastside Issaquah 1315 N
	W Mall Street\, Suite 4 Issaquah\, WA 98027 \\(next to the Gaslamp Bar & G
	rill\\)\n\n👥 Ages: 18\\+\n\n💸 Cost: $0.00 \\(yup\, totally free\\)\n\n🎯 Pr
	erequisite: No improv experience needed\n\n🚨 Max spots: 40 \\(Our regular 
	classes are smaller\, btw—12–16 students\\) \n\n✨ Ready to play\, explore\
	, and let go a little?\n\nSpots are limited\, so snag yours now and come s
	ee what the Unexpected is all about. \n\n\n\n\n\nRegister Here\n\nFrom SEA
	today - Arts & Culture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/free-introductory-improv-
	class-issaquah/17345422/2026-02-15T00
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley\, Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:em9xnxXQCQGxjsLgEUFAm
SUMMARY:Free Tax Help / Ayuda gratuita con los impuestos
DTSTAMP:20260214T003617Z
DTSTART:20260215T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Sunday\, February 15\, 2026\, 11am - 5pm\n\nTrained volunteers 
	will be available to answer questions and prepare personal tax returns.\n\
	nSpanish support may be provided per request.\n\n-------------------------
	---------------------------------------\n\nVoluntarios capacitados estarán
	 disponibles para responder preguntas y preparar declaraciones de impuesto
	s personales.\n\nSe puede proporcionar ayuda en español a pedido.\n\nLocat
	ion Link:\n\nSouth Park Branch\n\nRoom Location: Meeting Room / Sala de re
	uniones\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is not required / No se req
	uiere inscripción.\n\nDetailed Description: Drop-in tax help is offered on
	 a first-come\, first-served basis.\, This service is free and available t
	o individuals only.\, The free service is not available for business tax r
	eturns.\, To receive tax help\, bring the following documents:\,\n\nRequir
	ed Documents:\n\nPhoto identification\, Social Security cards or Individua
	l Taxpayer Identification Numbers \\(ITIN\\) for everyone listed on the ta
	x return\, Proof of income\, for example\, W2s and 1099s \\(Social Securit
	y benefits\\)\, Official documents on Social Security Administration lette
	rhead\, Medicare card \\(if Social Security number is followed by an "A"\\
	)\, Be prepared to provide information about health care coverage for each
	 person on the return\,\n\nRecommended:\n\nLast year&'s tax return\, if av
	ailable\, Bank account and routing numbers for direct deposit of refunds\,
	 Photocopies or computer print-outs of any of these documents will be acce
	pted.\, Due to federal budget cuts the IRS is unable to provide the Librar
	y with certain tax forms and instruction booklets.\, Most IRS forms are av
	ailable online at\n\nwww.irs.gov. \, You may make free black-and-white pri
	nts of the forms from Library computers:\n\nwww.spl.org/Print \, Thanks to
	 our partner\n\nUnited Way of King County .\,\n\n-------------------------
	---------------------------------------Se ofrece ayuda fiscal sin cita pre
	via por orden de llegada.\, Este servicio es gratuito y solo está disponib
	le para personas individuales.\, El servicio gratuito no está disponible p
	ara declaraciones de impuestos de empresas.\, Para recibir ayuda fiscal\, 
	traiga los siguientes documentos:\,\n\nDocumentos necesarios:\, Tarjetas d
	el Seguro Social o Números de Identificación Fiscal Individual \\(ITIN\\) 
	de todas las personas que figuran en la declaración de impuestos\, Prueba 
	de ingresos\, por ejemplo\, formularios W2 y 1099 \\(prestaciones del Segu
	ro Social\\)\, Documentos oficiales con membrete de la Administración del 
	Seguro Social\, Tarjeta de Medicare \\(si el número de Seguro Social va se
	guido de una "A"\\)\, Esté preparado para proporcionar información sobre l
	a cobertura sanitaria de cada persona que figura en la declaración.\,\n\nS
	e recomienda:\, La declaración de impuestos del año pasado\, si está dispo
	nible.\, Números de cuenta bancaria y de ruta para el depósito directo de 
	los reembolsos.\, Se aceptarán fotocopias o impresiones de computadora de 
	cualquiera de estos documentos.\, Debido a recortes presupuestarios federa
	les\, el IRS no puede proporcionar a la biblioteca ciertos formularios fis
	cales y folletos de instrucciones.\, La mayoría de los formularios del IRS
	 están disponibles en línea en\n\nwww.irs.gov .\, Puede imprimir los formu
	larios en blanco y negro de forma gratuita desde las computadoras de la bi
	blioteca:\n\nwww.spl.org/Imprimir \, Gracias a nuestro socio\n\nUnited Way
	 of King County .\n\nEvent Logistics: United Way Tax Help locations serve 
	anyone who earned less than $80\,000 in 2025 \\(or less than $96\,000 for 
	non-single filers\\).\, For eligibility details\, contact United Way at 20
	6-461-3700.\,\n\n---------------------------------------------------------
	-------Los centros de ayuda fiscal de United Way atienden a cualquier pers
	ona que haya ganado menos de 80\,000 dólares en 2025 \\(o menos de 96\,000
	 dólares para contribuyentes que no sean solteros\\).\, Para obtener más i
	nformación sobre los requisitos\, comuníquese con United Way al 206-461-37
	00\n\nContact Us: If you have questions about this event\,\n\nAsk Us\n\nor
	 call 206-386-4636.\,\n\n-------------------------------------------------
	---------------Si tiene alguna pregunta sobre este evento\,\n\npregúntenos
	\n\no llame al 206-386-4636.\n\nADA Accommodations: We can provide accommo
	dations for people with disabilities at Library events. Please\n\ncontactL
	EAP\n\nat least seven days before the event to request accommodations.\, A
	ll Library programs are free and open to the public.\,\n\n----------------
	------------------------------------------------Podemos ofrecer adaptacion
	es razonables para personas con discapacidad en los eventos de la bibliote
	ca. Póngase en contacto con\n\nLEAP\n\nal menos siete días antes del event
	o para solicitar las adaptaciones.\, Todos los programas de la biblioteca 
	son gratuitos y abiertos al público.\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/free-tax-help-ayuda-gratu
	ita-con-los-impuestos/18061697/2026-02-15T00
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT6H
END:VEVENT
