	------------------------------------------------------------\n\n万花筒边玩边学®: 
	孩子与他们的照顾者在小组中一起听多种语言故事、唱歌并做简单的手工。万花筒边玩边学®也是一个提供給孩子们探索各种玩具和游戏活动的时间。\n\n本次活动
	将以普通话和英语进行。\n\nLocation Link:\n\nBeacon Hill Branch\n\nRoom Location: Meet
	ing Room\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is not required / 注册不是必须的。
	\n\nDetailed Description: Kaleidoscope Play & Learn helps families prepare
	 their young children for success in school and life. This program\, reach
	es families in their neighborhoods and in their home languages weekly. Kid
	s and their caregivers take part in play activities that include stories\,
	 music\, game or crafts to support children&'s early learning.\, Community
	 services\, parenting education\, and child care resources available to he
	lp parents and caregivers raise healthy children.\, Thanks to our partners
	\n\nChinese Information and Service Center \\(CISC\\)\n\nand\n\nService Ce
	nter .\,\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------
	---------------------\, 雙語學前幼兒樂園活動協助家庭為幼兒提前適應學校和生活環境。每星期在不同的社區以家庭語言進行活動\,透
	過年齡適切的活動方式，包括遊戲﹑雙語兒歌﹑故事﹑手工﹑玩具等，支持兒童早期教學。\, 提供社區服務﹑家庭教育及育兒資源，讓幼兒家長及其照顧者培育健康
	活潑的孩子。\, 感謝我們的合作夥伴  Chinese Information and Service Center \\(CISC\\) 。\,\
	n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------
	------------\, 双语学前幼儿乐园活动协助家庭为幼儿提前适应学校和生活环境。每星期在不同的社区以家庭语言进行活动\,透过年龄适切的活动方
	式，包括游戏﹑双语儿歌﹑故事﹑手工﹑玩具等，支持儿童早期教学。\, 提供社区服务﹑家庭教育及育儿资源，让幼儿家长及其照顾者培育健康活泼的孩子。\, 
	感谢我们的合作伙伴  Chinese Information and Service Center \\(CISC\\) 。\,\n\nEvent 
	Logistics: This group is open to children of all abilities\, ages 0 to 5 y
	ears old.\, Kaleidoscope Play & Learn is for Family\, Friend & Neighbor Ca
	regivers\, Parents\, and the children in their care. This is not a drop-of
	f program and it is not agood fit for daycare centers\, preschools\, or ot
	her childcare organizations.\, Find out more about\n\nEarly Learning & Sto
	ry Time\n\nprograms.\,\n\n------------------------------------------------
	-----------------------------------\, 活動對象為0至5歲各種能力的兒童。萬花筒遊戲與學習 "適合家庭、朋友、鄰
