BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:cxQXAU1wWLf8OE8KkYNLL
SUMMARY:Clock-Out Lounge Presents: Spike Einbinder & Honey Pluton comedy to
	ur
DTSTAMP:20260214T003618Z
DTSTART:20260310T203000Z
DESCRIPTION:Clock-Out Lounge Presents:Spike Einbinder & Honey Pluton Tuesda
	y\\\, March 10th\\\, 8:00 PM doors21+$20adv/$25 dos Spike Einbinder and Ho
	ney Pluton hit the West Coast from NYC to split an hour of stand-up comedy
	! Expect transsexual musing\\\, tales of lore\\\, and hilarity ensuing. Ho
	ney Pluton is a stand-up comedian and theatrical performer with 10 years o
	f experience spanning stage\\\, film\\\, and screen. Hes creatively inspir
	ed by disruption\\\, risk-taking\\\, and the liminal thresholds that blur 
	states of consciousness. He is nationally touring his solo show Ive Always
	 Been Like This to sold-out crowds across the country and is also the host
	 of the weekly podcast Up Good with Honey Pluton. Spike Einbinder is a com
	edian\\\, actor\\\, writer\\\, drag performer\\\, and 6\\\,000-year-old sh
	apeshifting demon from Los Angeles. His work combines body horror\\\, surr
	ealism\\\, and dark comedy. He has featured roles in HBOs Los Espookys\\\,
	 as well as A24s You Hurt My Feelings and Problemista. He has performed hi
	s live solo comedy hours Visions and Im Not Scared m Not Insane to sold-ou
	t crowds.\n\nFrom Clock-Out Lounge
URL:https://clockoutlounge.com/event/clock-out-lounge-presents-spike-einbin
